venue.name: Eye of the Hawk Rye Dream Class

item.description:
Join AJ Kitt, founder of the Seacoast Paranormal Research Group and the Kitt Research Initiative, in an interactive open format discussion about metaphysics and how it applies to day to day life. With real-world hints and techniques, you are bound to walk away with a fresh perspective on how to get the things you want that seem to be eluding you! While drop-ins are welcome, preregistration is appreciated by calling (603) 964-7874.

Fee is by donation!
item.name: Lecture - "Wish Fulfillment"
